{"tid":96948,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"將黑人變黃皮膚 外國網民怒斥美圖秀秀種族歧視","createTime":"2017-01-27T09:37:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-27T13:02:59.000Z","uid":65710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9456e21f3a8cfeb13bd860a489d5a1c1c5023234","tid":96948,"uid":65710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T09:37:33.000Z","msg":"美圖秀秀的手繪特效最近大熱，吸引不少網民試玩，將自己的自拍照改頭換面。有網民發現美圖秀秀會將用戶的手機資料傳到大陸的伺服器，擔心出現安全問題，後來美圖秀秀需要作出解釋。手繪特效功能紅到外國，很多人不理手機資料安全問題試玩，但又帶出了另一個問題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/jxk0vht3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fjxk0vht3&h=7d2b3c44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有外國網民試玩其手繪特效功能後，表示無論導入的相片是黑人還是白人，軟件都只會將相中人變成了黃皮膚，認為美圖秀秀存在種族歧視。有網民表示美圖秀秀是為黃種人製作，非亞裔人應該拒絕使用。美圖秀秀原本就是以大陸用戶作為主要對象，而特效本身亦沒有讓用戶調整膚色的選項，難怪會出現黑人變白的情況。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/w62ipvak\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fw62ipvak&h=f017f435&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/01/25/meitu-was-blamed-racist/software/android-app/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2Fmeitu-was-blamed-racist%2Fsoftware%2Fandroid-app%2F&d=T1%2FbvXP8%2Bo0cJI4QM9OX2xpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=e37b17fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/01/25/meitu-was-blamed-racist/software/android-app/</a>"},{"pid":"1548b27cb00370b942da689808d8c92950d04076","tid":96948,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T09:40:52.000Z","msg":"左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"070244bb5e0fda0ef0940dce9474d1b62dcb1d03